设置某服务开机自动启动: #syatemctl enable xxx.service
设置某服务开机不自动启动： #systemctl disable xxx.service
查询服务详细状态信息: #systemctl status xxx.service
显示服务是否启动: #systemctl is-active xxx.service
显示所有已启动的服务: #systemctl list-units --type=service
启动某服务: #syatemctl start xxx.service
关闭某服务: #systemctl stop xxx.service
重启某服务: #syatemctl restart xxx.service
